{"tid":1270073,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再花力氣感化班廢老","createTime":"2019-06-30T18:10:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T18:28:10.000Z","uid":201178,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9ef02097eabcb68bec48ba16d53429834281f9c6","tid":1270073,"uid":201178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T18:10:10.000Z","msg":"廢老之所以係廢老，就因為<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">缺乏思考能力</div></span></span><br />\n<br />\n大部分廢老都係大陸落黎，書都唔讀多本，<br />\n根本<span style=\"color: gold;\">[size=5]process唔到咩係逃犯條例[/size=5</span>]，<br />\n遑論民主自由呢堆理念。<br />\n<br />\n由今日遊行就睇到，69到宜家都一個月，<br />\n佢地都搞唔清條例係做乜，<br />\n由頭到本住廢老名言<span style=\"color: red;\">「宜家啲人點點點」</span>去<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">盲目反後生仔</span></span>，再鳩講「唔犯法就冇事」去支持自己。<br />\n<br />\n面對咁既廢老，解釋再多只係浪費自己心機。<br />\n所以，唔好感化，<br />\n直接<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">令佢討厭香港政府。</div></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n例如咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/37DTJQn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F37DTJQn.png&h=574c6422&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就係呢張圖，我媽媽已經不再廢老。<br />\n我媽媽得，你地都得。"},{"pid":"dff10f1f7322990187c8a3271a4f01afebcf4e9f","tid":1270073,"uid":201178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T18:16:00.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"70d76a432fd80c0c6a0e22d7f81de7927a6e54d0","tid":1270073,"uid":201178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T18:28:10.000Z","msg":"自推"}]}